==Awards==
* Spanish ''[[Medalla de la Campaña]]''{{sfn|Berger|1999|p=199}}
* Spanish ''[[Medalla Militar]]''{{sfn|Berger|1999|p=199}}
* [[Spanish Cross]] in Gold with Swords and Diamonds (6 July 1939){{sfn|Berger|1999|p=199}}
* [[Wound Badge]] in Black{{sfn|Berger|1999|p=199}}
* [[Front Flying Clasp of the Luftwaffe]] in Gold with Pennant "300"{{sfn|Berger|1999|p=199}}
* [[Combined Pilots-Observation Badge]] in Gold with Diamonds{{sfn|Berger|1999|p=199}}
* [[Iron Cross]] (1939)
** 2nd Class (26 May 1940){{sfn|Thomas|1998|p=46}}
** 1st Class (3 June 1940){{sfn|Thomas|1998|p=46}}
* [[Knight's Cross of the Iron Cross with Oak Leaves and Swords]]
** Knight's Cross on 18 September 1940 as ''[[Major (Germany)|Major]]'' and ''[[Geschwaderkommodore]]'' of ''Jagdgeschwader'' 3{{sfn|Scherzer|2007|p=519}}
** 27th Oak Leaves on 20 July 1941 as ''Major'' and ''Geschwaderkommodore'' of ''Jagdgeschwader'' 3{{sfn|Scherzer|2007|p=519}}
** 4th Swords on 11 October 1941 as ''Major'' and ''Geschwaderkommodore'' of ''Jagdgeschwader'' 3{{sfn|Scherzer|2007|p=519}}
* Mentioned in the ''[[Wehrmachtbericht]]''

